title: Amazon Best Books of the Month - January 2018 [epub]
description:
Hand-picked reads from the Amazon Books Editors. For anyone looking for a good book to read on your couch or the subway, this list is a good place to start your search.


01. The Immortalists by Chloe Benjamin
02. Need to Know by Karen Cleveland
03. The Woman in the Window by A. J. Finn
04. The Largesse of the Sea Maiden by Denis Johnson
05. Here Is Real Magic by Nate Staniforth
06. Oliver Loving by Stefan Merrill Block
07. The Road Not Taken by Max Boot
08. The Widows of Malabar Hill by Sujata Massey
09. When: The Scientific Secrets of Perfect Timing by Daniel H. Pink
10. Green by Sam Graham-Felsen
